scenario_text.value:
We did it... We won! We totally won!
Absolutely incredible!
But...what am I going to do with this...?

Saki, do you...not like the way I look? Is
it...weird?
What? No! That’s... That’s not it at all...
Well...it sounds to me like it is.

I mean, I can’t say I expected this. It’s
a bit...sharper? Than I expected?

B-but, hey! It’s only just barely outside my
expectations, so! Aha...haha.

*ahem*... Anyway... You’re the whole reason
we won!
That I can appreciate. Yeah... Thanks.
Aww, stop picking on my semantics!

I’m super duper grateful, really I am! I’m
totally counting on you, mkay?!
